Okay so you have started learning SQL or maybe you are looking this for the future job oppurtunities .
After learning SQL there are plenty of jobs that you can apply for the most High paying and the most responsible job 
is the job of the Database Administrator(DBA),the who manages the complete database . 
The one who has almost complete control over the database such as , he/she can grant access to anyone the permission to access 
the contents of the databasae and can even revoke these permisiions. Moreover, DBA has complete control over the data and can make
any kind of futile changes in the database . So, that is why it is one of the most paying jobs out there.

Secondly, you can apply for the post of database maintenance, it is not much rewarding as compared to DBA . But this one is easier 
to get as compared to DBA.
